                        <interp inst="t18380101-name-497" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES PEARSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep the Portland Arms, Portland-street, Maryle. bone. I was at dinner on the 27th of December, and received information that two men were seen to take pots from the door—I and my pot-boy went out, and fell in with the prisoner—I took him—he was taken to the office, but I did not go with him—this pot was found on him at the office—it had been on the railing at my door.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I did not take the pot—I found it inside a bag that a man had dropped.</p>
